title: Price index : Desktop and similar computers in Canada 2018
summary: The graph shows the Price index Desktop similar computers in Canada during 2018 .
The values are described using the ID 384 ( FPPI ) .
gold: As it can be seen from the graph , the price index about desktop and similar computer in Canada during 2018 slowly decreased over the year with several fluctuations . During January and February the values remain stable , without any changes . The minimum values have been recorded during August and October .
